thread.title: P Currie
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by P Currie

author: P Currie
title: P Currie
text:
We had a good experience with Omega. Friendly service by the young lady in the office. She was helpful explaining how to get into the city etc.
No fault with the car. Transfer driver was a bit late getting back to make our flight, so somebody took us to the airport.
Only down part was, it would have been nice if transfer driver had helped us (3 ladies) with their bags into the van on arrival, rather than standing watching us do it.
